{"tid":1457432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我宣佈 全部手足唔準屌散水撚！！","createTime":"2019-08-12T11:42:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T16:39:30.000Z","uid":201604,"like":112,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"f92abfa8455ab90ac7d25dc2bf24285ba7109354","tid":1457432,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:42:21.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">反省完 下次大家就識做 唔分化！！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家都覺得 機場集會係會好和平<br />\n而且大家都好嬲<br />\n所以今日有好多新手bb都有去 甚至係第一次出黎<br />\n<br />\n睇住popo冇底線<br />\n各位新手好易就嚇親 一驚就亂<br />\n又會傳消息叫人走 希望大家唔好出事<br />\n最後搞到好心做壞事<br />\n但都唔使屌佢地 只需要教佢地<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">冷靜啲 認清事實 勿亂傳 勿誇大</span></strong><br />\n尤其是越黎越多鬼 確認資訊真係好重要！！<br />\n<br />\n當然今日亦都有真三毛<br />\n機場集會搞到對面咁努力帶風向<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>證明我地一定要再去機場</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n記住不割蓆 不分化 不互屌<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"b6a2b9448597685732b6b16841adf707aefe1b18","tid":1457432,"uid":126868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:42:35.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"fc67c44fa87126ee4baff78c5375e2ed26a73ebe","tid":1457432,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:42:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd43b8341ddbb43255910acb2e2f5969fd3168c5","tid":1457432,"uid":212182,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:43:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bpz2ope.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbpz2ope.jpg&h=74c62a67&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n唔好再鬧人散，做得唔好反省下次做更好，內訌係無意思！！"},{"pid":"ff5df50492d92864cddb4028f087f8678e44e4ac","tid":1457432,"uid":293698,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:43:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"50a33181ec8d8f338cf880d6ace58dfa748065fa","tid":1457432,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:44:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6f5e9f0dc2c61b87c2374732f45f18f52e4930f",